Time Train No. Print this Page Beijing - Shanghai Train Schedule Departing toFrom Since it is opened to traffic in June 2011, the Beijing-Shanghai high-speed rail enables high-speed trains to get to Shanghai from Beijing within 5 hours. Now many passengers would choose to go to Shanghai from Beijing by high-speed train. Every day, the scheduled trains depart from Beijing South Railway Station and arrive at Shanghai Hongqiao Railway Station. Here, China Highlights offers Beijing-Shanghai train schedule for you to seek a train from Beijing to Shanghai. China Highlights provides Beijing-Shanghai train schedule with a list of trains going to Shanghai from Beijing.
